# Static archive of GameCon 2001 (reconstructed from the Internet Archive).
#
# GameCon 2001 ran in OLOMOUC (per Wikipedia). It was a SECTION of the whole
# altar.cz publisher site (path altar.cz/gamecon/), the same path-era as
# 2002-2005 — older than the gamecon.altar.cz subdomain (2006-2008).
#
# IMPORTANT — this is a MINIMAL, honest archive. Wayback never preserved a
# genuine GameCon 2001 festival site (no gamecon.cz domain or subdomain existed
# then; the only 2001-window homepage capture is the OFF-SEASON placeholder,
# still showing the 2000 recap and "informace o Gameconu 2001 zatím nejsou k
# dispozici"). What genuinely survives, and is served here:
#   - the homepage as captured (the honest 2001 off-season state),
#   - the Mistrovství v DrD RESULTS: vysledky01 (real 2001 results, from a 2004
#     capture) + vysledky98/99/00,
#   - the Altar publisher-site nav menu (2001-window captures) + era theme.
# The 2001 program/tournament pages were never published/captured — they 404.
#
# Pages restored from web.archive.org, transcoded WINDOWS-1250 -> UTF-8 (with an
# injected <meta charset>; the source declared charset only via the HTTP header).
# Dead ad embeds (billboard.cz, eReklama) stripped. Dynamic CGI -> themed 404.

DirectoryIndex index.html
ErrorDocument 404 /404.html

Options -Indexes

<IfModule mod_rewrite.c>
    RewriteEngine On

    RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} -f
    RewriteRule ^ - [L]

    RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} -d
    RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME}/index.html -f
    RewriteRule ^ - [L]

    RewriteRule ^$  index.html [L]

    RewriteRule ^.*$ - [R=404,L]
</IfModule>
